# Pep8 Violations Galore: The not so good, the quite bad and the seriously ugly<!--more -->


During the deep dive for release 0.0.2. Two things stood out like a sore thumbs, the gratuitous use of lambda functions
and Decimals.

## Sinful use of Lambdas

